A <strong>graphical front-end</strong> called Asmee (ASM Eclipse Environment) which allows to edit and manipulate AsmM models. This environment is implemented as eclipse plug-in.

### Eclipse plugin
The editor is available as eclipse plugin. Follow the instructions [here](./index.html#installing-asmeta-in-eclipse)

